        "Where the per-frequency progress signal gamma(f, t) comes from. 'approximation' is self-contained but uniform across bands, so the frequency shaping comes entirely from the alpha-tilt parameters. 'matrix' uses the precomputed per-band gamma for true spectral-bias-aware coloring (more noise to genuinely under-resolved bands).",
      enum: ['matrix', 'approximation'],
